{"tid":814468,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"莫斯科拍板興建「紙片高樓」","createTime":"2018-09-11T09:11:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-09-11T09:23:27.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"d6289a99cc18754d320806a537d3e988b0b1fd4c","tid":814468,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T09:11:47.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180911/20496607\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180911%2F20496607&d=zprXbIA%2Fr9l9%2BaN0GqaKwleK4D04he4k8uKHxpzC8zE%3D&h=fafe2870\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20180911%2F20496607&h=0e0e655d\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/daily/article/20180911/20496607</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年09月11日 <br />\n<br />\n莫斯科拍板興建「紙片高樓」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20180911/large/11wx64p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20180911%2Flarge%2F11wx64p.jpg&h=5c6239f6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n尚未命名的未來莫斯科第一高樓外形如紙片。互聯網<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n繼聖彼得堡的拉赫塔中心，俄羅斯莫斯科當局亦開綠燈，批准興建全首都最高的摩天大廈。這幢纖薄而高聳入雲的建築尚在設計階段，料2019年會開始動工，2024年竣工後會成為全歐洲第二高的大廈。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n僅寬32米呈梯形<br />\n<br />\n大廈由俄羅斯建築師事務所謝爾蓋．斯庫拉托夫（Sergey Skuratov）設計，共有109層、高404米，將會屹立於首都最繁忙商業區莫斯科城。大廈最底的12層會作購物中心、辦公室及其他商業用途，上方的92層則主要作住宅用途。最高的樓層會作觀景台及直升機停機坪之用。<br />\n<br />\n有別長方形的傳統外形，大廈呈僅寬32米的梯形，迎面對着莫斯科河。建築師斯庫拉托指大廈的外觀會予人一種「白色漸退之感」，大樓下層會是白色，上層漸變為藍色。<br />\n<br />\n莫斯科城現時已經高樓林立，歐洲10大最高建築物中有五幢大廈皆屹立於此，包括該市之前的最高樓、高373米的聯邦塔（Federal Tower）。現仍有不少發展商在區內大興土木，不久將有10多座摩天大廈相繼落成。<br />\n<br />\n斯庫拉托夫認為，該區多幢新建大樓風格，跟原來建築群不大相襯。他指「氾濫的新建築物令整個區域欠缺和諧。在我而言，它們都過於複雜，設計沒有考慮到對其他建築物的影響」。他又指「不幸地，這裏沒有統一的佈局，或原始的意念」。<br />\n<br />\n美國有線新聞網絡  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n上一則<br />\n上一則<br />\n俄拉赫塔中心　傲視歐洲<br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n鬥起摩天樓　上海中心全球第二高<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n鬥起摩天樓　上海中心全球第二高<br />\n<br />\n俄染指巴黎建「冬宮」　居民遭逼遷<br />\n<br />\n俄拉赫塔中心　傲視歐洲"},{"pid":"10635892faa692c0f8c8b14ab0926f738213c4e3","tid":814468,"uid":65603,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T09:15:00.000Z","msg":"On9設計<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a724aa9113c20c0ec0d5763a3541b13e96b5097","tid":814468,"uid":111814,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T09:18:58.000Z","msg":"真正既屏風樓<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06b027ed55772fe4b9381790945221cc8bef8f95","tid":814468,"uid":53672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T09:19:06.000Z","msg":"幾型既"},{"pid":"51ca08d7bbc236164c3728ee906b5233596fc1c1","tid":814468,"uid":4739,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T09:20:49.000Z","msg":"北韓一早有啦"},{"pid":"613db41b156f02b3e30e857954e44473196a5d7f","tid":814468,"uid":51200,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T09:21:43.000Z","msg":"起係香港，一打風應該打橫訓低"},{"pid":"06958289adb52ae6ef5265935e31b74a9f7a4474","tid":814468,"uid":62532,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T09:22:26.000Z","msg":"班engineer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n用32 米moment arm黎頂晒d windload , 好想知個foundation同column點design"},{"pid":"1715add79b95bf195ddb113e155b3a719e5f2a63","tid":814468,"uid":28599,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-11T09:23:27.000Z","msg":"404米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n玩命建築"}]}